__NAME__ purpose
encrypt credit card information automatically
__END__


__NAME__ see also
EncryptProgram, PGP
__END__

__NAME__ synopsis
<group choice='plain'>
	<arg choice='plain'>No</arg>
	<arg choice='plain'>Yes</arg>
</group>
__END__


__NAME__ description
The directive enables automatic encryption and saving of credit card
information.
</para><para>
The &conf-EncryptProgram; directive must be configured and working first.
__END__

__NAME__ example: Defining __FILENAME__
<programlisting>
CreditCardAuto Yes
</programlisting>
__END__

__NAME__ missing
